cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.CR 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with training neural networks. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) for the same reason. Additionally, since the paper focuses on robustness against adversarial attacks, it could belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, since the paper deals with image datasets, it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
